'''凌日系外行星巡天衛星'''（{{lang-en|'''T'''ransiting '''E'''xoplanet '''S'''urvey '''S'''atellite}}，縮寫簡稱'''TESS'''，中國大陸又簡稱為'''苔丝'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.kepuchina.cn/wiki/yzts/04/201907/t20190731_1088755.shtml |title=“苔丝”探测器发现3颗太阳系外行星 |accessdate=2019-08-03 |archive-date=2019-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803114054/https://www.kepuchina.cn/wiki/yzts/04/201907/t20190731_1088755.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是[[美國國家航空暨太空總署|美國國家航空暨太空總署]][[探索者計劃|探索者計劃]]中的[[太空望遠鏡|太空望遠鏡]]，旨在使用[[系外行星偵測法#凌日法|凌日法]]在比[[克卜勒太空望遠鏡|克卜勒太空望遠鏡]]覆蓋的區域大400倍的區域內搜索[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]<ref name="Ricker">{{cite journal | title=Transiting Exoplanet Survey Satellite | date=2014-10-24 | publisher = SPIE Digital Library | doi=10.1117/1.JATIS.1.1.014003 | last1=Ricker | first1=George R. | last2=Winn | first2=Joshua N. | last3=Vanderspek | first3=Roland | last4=Latham | first4=David W. | last5=Bakos | first5=Gáspár Á. | last6=Bean | first6=Jacob L. | last7=Berta-Thompson | first7=Zachory K. | last8=Brown | first8=Timothy M. | last9=Buchhave | first9=Lars | last10=Butler | first10=Nathaniel R. | last11=Butler | first11=R. Paul | last12=Chaplin | first12=William J. | last13=Charbonneau | first13=David | last14=Christensen-Dalsgaard | first14=Jørgen | last15=Clampin | first15=Mark | last16=Deming | first16=Drake | last17=Doty | first17=John | last18=De Lee | first18=Nathan | last19=Dressing | first19=Courtney | last20=Dunham | first20=Edward W. | last21=Endl | first21=Michael | last22=Fressin | first22=Francois | last23=Ge | first23=Jian | last24=Henning | first24=Thomas | last25=Holman | first25=Matthew J. | last26=Howard | first26=Andrew W. | last27=Ida | first27=Shigeru | last28=Jenkins | first28=Jon M. | last29=Jernigan | first29=Garrett | last30=Johnson | first30=John Asher | journal=Journal of Astronomical Telescopes, Instruments, and Systems | volume=1 | page=014003 | display-authors=29 | doi-access=free }}</ref>。它於2018年4月18日由[[獵鷹9號|獵鷹9號]]火箭發射升空，並被置於繞地球的高度橢圓的13.7天的軌道上<ref name="Ricker"/><ref name="sfn-schedule">{{cite web |url=https://spaceflightnow.com/launch-schedule/ |title=Launch Schedule |work=Spaceflight Now |date=February 27, 2018 |access-date=February 28, 2018 |archive-date=2018-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816161152/https://spaceflightnow.com/launch-schedule/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nasa.gov">{{cite web |url=https://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-planet-hunter-on-its-way-to-orbit |title=NASA Planet Hunter on Its Way to Orbit |date=April 19, 2018 |website=NASA |access-date=April 19, 2018 |archive-date=2022-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220214151412/https://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-planet-hunter-on-its-way-to-orbit/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

凌日系外行星巡天衛星的主要任務目標是調查地球附近300光年內的恆星是否有[[行星|行星]]存在。凌日系外行星巡天衛星將可能研究一大群小型行星，包括在其宿主恆星的可居住區、行星的質量、大小、密度及軌道。凌日系外行星巡天衛星將提供[[詹姆斯·韋伯太空望遠鏡|詹姆斯·韋伯太空望遠鏡]]以及未來的其他太空或地面望遠鏡進一步觀測的目標。

凌日系外行星巡天衛星將觀測明亮恆星附近的小型行星，記錄最鄰近的及最明亮的[[主序星|主序星]]<ref name="NASA-2014">{{cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/files/NASA_2015_Budget_Estimates.pdf |format=PDF |title=NASA FY 2015 President's Budget Request Summary |publisher=NASA |date=2014-03-10 |accessdate=2016-08-02 |archive-date=2016-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423094736/http://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/files/NASA_2015_Budget_Estimates.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年9月，凌日系外行星巡天衛星在[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]]與[[谷歌|谷歌]][[種子基金|種子基金]]的帶領下<ref name="chandler-2008">{{cite web |url=http://newsoffice.mit.edu/2008/mit-aims-search-earth-planets-googles-help |title=MIT aims to search for Earth-like planets with Google's help |work=MIT News |first=David |last=Chandler |date=2008-03-19 |accessdate=2016-08-02 |archive-date=2014-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217231300/http://newsoffice.mit.edu/2008/mit-aims-search-earth-planets-googles-help |dead-url=no }}</ref>，入選美國國家航空暨太空總署資助的計畫提案之一<ref name="study">{{cite press release |url=http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/sep/HQ_11-328_Science_Proposals.html |title=NASA Selects Science Investigations For Concept Studies |publisher=NASA |first=Dwayne |last=Brown |date=2011-09-29 |access-date=2016-08-02 |archive-date=2016-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160804053626/http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/sep/HQ_11-328_Science_Proposals.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年4月5日，美國國家航空暨太空總署宣布凌日系外行星巡天衛星將隨著要裝設在[[國際太空站|國際太空站]]上的{{link-en|中子星內部組成探測器|Neutron Star Interior Composition Explorer}}（Neutron Star Interior Composition Explorer）一同在2018年發射<ref name="selection">{{cite press release |url=http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2013/apr/HQ_13-088_Astro_Explorer_Mission_.html |title=NASA Selects Explorer Investigations for Formulation |publisher=NASA |first=J. D. |last=Harrington |date=2013-04-05 |access-date=2016-08-02 |archive-date=2016-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617075215/http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2013/apr/HQ_13-088_Astro_Explorer_Mission_.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MIT">{{cite web |url=http://newsoffice.mit.edu/2013/nasa-selects-tess-for-mission-0405 |title=NASA selects MIT-led TESS project for 2017 mission |work=MIT News |date=2013-04-05 |accessdate=2013-04-06 |archive-date=2015-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801201529/http://newsoffice.mit.edu/2013/nasa-selects-tess-for-mission-0405 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不過最後中子星內部組成探測器卻比凌